data.name: rzxFinaliseToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Ends the recording session. The file cannot be used to continue recording later.

data.name: rzxDiscardToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Ends current session without saving any recorded data.

data.name: rzxStopToolStripMenuItem1.ToolTipText
data.value: Stops current session, but you can continue recording at a later time.

data.name: rzxInsertBookmarkToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value:
Inserts a bookmark that will allow the RZX recording to be rolled back to.
The TAB key can also be used to insert bookmarks if your keyboard doesn't have the INS key.

data.name: rzxRollbackToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Rolls back a recording to a previous bookmark.

data.name: programFinderToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Search for titles online using ZXDB.
